    <lb n="12"/>ἀλόγως, <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να μηδὲ τὰ ἀν

    <lb n="13" type="worddiv"/>αλώματα ἀπαιτήσω σε. 

    <lb n="14"/><supplied reason="lost">ἔ</supplied><unclear>ρρ</unclear>ωσ<unclear>ο</unclear>. </ab></div></body></text></TEI.2>